    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Maps used by insurance companies and emergency management agencies such as FEMA in assessing risk to property. In conservation and heritage management contexts, maps used in vulnerability analysis, assessing risk to cultural heritage areas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
